snippet.title: Naval Warfare - Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
"Naval Warfare" is a stylish steampunk naval-action shooter with numerous tactical elements. Steer your ship into the middle of a raging naval war, where masses of enemies and allies engage in real-time operations over large, multi-screen maps. The game is driven by an entertaining story-campaign with beautiful hand-drawn comics and features a unique, distinctive steampunk art-style.

more information on www.layernet.de
